<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.4">
<l>uḻantāḷ naṟuneyyō rōrtaṭā vuṇṇa</l>
<l>viḻantā ḷeriviṉā līrtteḻil mattiṉ</l>
<l>paḻantāmpā lōccap payattāl tavaḻntāṉ</l>
<l>muḻantā ḷiruntavā kāṇīrē mukiḻmulai yīrvantu kāṇīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with bud[-like] breasts, see the way the knees are of he who</l>
<l>crept [away] in terror [after he] ate each and every pot of the ghee</l>
<l>of she who suffered and she who lost [the ghee] dragged [him] with anger</l>
<l>and raised the old rope of a big churning stick to strike [him]. Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
